                                                                                                                                                                                            <p>If we make material changes to the way we use personal information, before they take effect, we will notify you by posting a notice of these changes prominently on our sites or notify you via email if you have provided us that information. Please review our Privacy Policy periodically to learn how we are collecting, using and sharing your information.</p>
